Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.57,0:00:10.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be the other you that I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:18.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere beyond this sky is a girl with wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:21.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She spreads those wings and continues to be blown by the wind from the distant past,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:23.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just like long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:28.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother passed away before she told me any more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:44.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, my only companions whilst traveling have been that story of the girl in the sky and this doll.
Comment: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:44.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,TRIPLE LINE NOOOO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:49.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, are you also searching for the same girl as your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:52.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no way that you're that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:54.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people dream of flying through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl can fly too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:00:59.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:01.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She has wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:04.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had wings too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, freeloader, here's a present for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a sloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:10.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this cuter than that dirty doll of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:13.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I need to have you make some money so you can get out of here ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.84,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:25.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing like a drink after work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I live for these times!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:33.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, freeloader, first up tonight is touching love confessions that bring a tear to the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:35.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Entertain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Misuzu, are you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:43.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here. You can use my lap as a pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:47.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! I-It's okay. I'm not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:51.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:04.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you let her use your lap as a pillow a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:09.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As if that girl would cuddle up to someone as pathetic as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say "gao" again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I whacked her each time she said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:25.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When she was little, she thought chicks were baby dinosaurs for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:31.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so when she saw the chicks at a summer fair, she begged for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were so poor then; we couldn't buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:41.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, she learned to say "gao" whenever something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out to be a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have stayed alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, that girl is a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:56.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she seems to cheer up when she's with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so if possible, I hope you'll stay friends with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more I can do for her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:46.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! It's time for a fun puppet show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:58.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like something you might see in a dream... I mean a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:03.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on; let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my payment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:15.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name was Potato, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikkori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:28.52,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pika piko piko pika piko pikopiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.52,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your daughter well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:36.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She says white rice tastes great and asks for seconds and thirds, so it makes cooking worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:40.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell her to be careful of an upset stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:42.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:50.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing loitering in front of my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:54.14,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikapikapika piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:54.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go home, shall we...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.42,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't ignore me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:59.26,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko! Piko! Piko! Piko! Piko! Piiikoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Potato. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:05.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun is talking with Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.03,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz357.838\c&H0E0D0C&\pos(667,223)}KIRISHIMA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.03,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz357.838\c&H0E0D0C&\pos(1032,239)}CLINIC
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:10.63,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikopiko pi-pikopiko piko piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:12.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:15.93,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Potato's become your fan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you say your name is Yukito Kunisaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:23.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skill is impressive, but I doubt you'll be able to make much money with that trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:23.88,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:25.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:31.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I've been traveling from town to town using this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:36.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean you've made lots of money in this town too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:45.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be interested in working at this clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Hijiri Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since my parents passed away, I'm the only doctor in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been looking for someone to do odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:57.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why bamboo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you eating nagashi soumen for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this house, if Kano asks for nagashi soumen, we eat nagashi soumen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.14,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:15.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, this is an unfair seating arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:15.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd eat a lot if you didn't sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:20.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you tomorrow at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay me better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:31.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, as an added benefit, I'll let you put on your puppet shows in front of my clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:34.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry; I'll let you eat lunch too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play again tomorrow, Yukito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:38.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko! Pikooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was taking that job a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this town really doesn't have many people walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess traffic accidents are rare too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:09:00.01,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(643,60)\fsp2.25\c&H0E0D0C&}NIINUMA  RICE  AND  LIQUOR  SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no. It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:04.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:07.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault too for bumping into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you have so much stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:13.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter loves rice and eats so much of it that I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:18.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:24.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much, but please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't anyone in this town use actual money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:33.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what kind of girl can eat that much rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a sloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a smaller version of Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:08.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened to your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:12.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:18.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:24.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yummy and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide whether it's yummy or cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:29.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute and yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:34.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san, who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Six-years-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What an incredible name!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you say before your age, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika Shino, six-years-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:52.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:11:00.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that girl has to be admitted to hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:02.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't seem too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:10.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And she said the sloth has become her friend, so she'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:12.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:26.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a dream about the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:32.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a world I'd never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:41.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See, when you sit like this, the clouds are above you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:46.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in my dream, the clouds were beneath my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:49.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Between the clouds, I could see the bright blue of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:54.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't tell how far it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything extended endlessly into infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,did you have wings in your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:08.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:13.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't go around telling people about such dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:17.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it fits you well somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a different one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest are all too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, it smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I put all my effort into it, so it's exceedingly delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A boxed lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to the trouble just for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please deliver it to Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:53.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:56.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano is at school again taking care of the animals today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you dare eat it on the way there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it carefully and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop by the bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are quite a lot of students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they're here for remedial classes, club activities, or student government.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:13.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:18.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be a good place to set up shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:17.86,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:21.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please welcome my puppet show with lots of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.53,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&HDEDEDE&\move(523,97,543,132,0,2692)}YUKITO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.53,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&HDEDEDE&\frz0\move(787,99,764,134,0,2692)}FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.53,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H7E7468&\frz20.715\move(49,544,123,524,22,2692)}KUNI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.53,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H7E7468&\frz340.085\move(211,535,262,516,22,2692)}SAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Love and Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:34.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that'll ever happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:34.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:35.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:36.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:41.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take this weird creature in, the high school might erupt in a great panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:46.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move from here until I tell you it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:50.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to deliver a boxed lunch to Kano Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano-rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:59.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano-rin... Maybe she's still in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to the rooftop because she wanted some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:08.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "kyuu," and collapsed all of a sudden after mumbling something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she just got a little light-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is so high, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun, can't you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can move a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That has absolutely nothing to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:48.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, didn't you say something about if you could use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not completely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use it until I grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:15:00.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've already decided what I'll do with my first spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:05.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what I'll do second, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't particularly want to hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:11.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't listen, it'll claw its way out of your stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and turn into something so strong that mankind can't even fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:16.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Earth, the Earth is in great trouble!" Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:16.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to protect the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the second thing you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:22.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fly through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic to fly through the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't attack me so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:43.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And after I went through the trouble of calling out to you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:47.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My head is spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a dirty doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so tattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're suffering under a stupid master, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:56.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that so poignantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:59.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.72,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.69,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&HF3F3F3&\pos(679,126)\frz359.5}SHIMANO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.69,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(863,129)\frz359.216\c&HF3F3F3&}BOOKSTORE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a Butt Swayling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:17.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:25.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:36.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to have Minagi fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to act so high and mighty?!
Comment: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ALTERNATIVE: Who are you to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:40.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's all nice now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.60,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:49.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a very precious doll to you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since you are always carrying it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the physical form of a precious memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:07.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.86,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I present you with a coupon for rice.
