Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:13.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:16.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Tohno-san great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:31.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is she good at her studies, but she's good at sewing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:32.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:35.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:37.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A place where lots of people gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:42.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put on your puppet show there, you'll have many customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:43.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:44.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:47.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what kind of work does she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she went to pray at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:52.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's where we're headed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:00.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be full of people then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of kids from town will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids in this town are all unruly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Waah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:13.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:18.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're here, I thought we could play some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:24.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How old do you think we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then... let's catch bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:42.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:46.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care what we play, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:49.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer vacation, so I want to play as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:02.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:26.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, do you still believe that when a chick grows up, it'll become a dinosaur?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:29.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Geez, I know already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:32.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chicks grow up to be chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:38.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, what I really wanted wasn't a chick or a baby dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I heard that you cried all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:48.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It didn't matter what it was, as long as Mommy bought it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fun day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:55.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:20:01.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had so much fun on my birthday before, so I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's... your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you keep quiet about something that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:09.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:12.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd known, I would've tried to buy you a present at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:12.27,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\frz343.316\pos(853,734)}Rice\NCoupon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:12.44,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\frz342.809\pos(810,571)}Rice\NCoupon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:12.56,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\frz344.93\pos(783,492)}Rice\NCoupon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.52,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\frz343.578\pos(769,450)}Rice\NCoupon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:26.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one would watch a puppet show at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you done for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:29.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me something, even if it's just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:41.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:46.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't suppose kids would be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:47.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to visit some friends, but they weren't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:58.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A thank-you gift for showing me something so unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:10.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lucky that I was given a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:14.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, and the number of candles was just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:17.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he was planning to celebrate someone's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:22.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Haruko remember that today is your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:24.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's busy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:37.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:44.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:45.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:47.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:51.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:54.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:59.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the number of stars in the heavens,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:02.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the number of trees in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:04.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the number...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:05.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.81,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(400,900)\fs51\shad2.25\pos(641,293)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:43.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least work enough to earn your wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:45.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:47.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:48.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:50.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:52.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:55.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many mysteries in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:57.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she always weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:59.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.11,0:24:01.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if there's nothing, then it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:02.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:04.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.57,0:24:05.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:07.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it well at all!
