Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:18.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko! Pik-
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.26,0:01:33.41,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}We watched the fading vapor trails
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.96,0:01:37.86,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}They were so dazzling, I ran away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.87,0:01:47.24,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}I was so frustrated, I released your hand
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.97,0:01:55.09,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}The place she can't reach is still there in the distance
